CustomField.description: Defines if a second set of 'Break' fields are active for use on Timesheets via the Timesheet Manager, Employee Portal and Approver Pages. When FALSE, there will only be one set of Break fields available on Timesheets.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines if a second set of 'Break' fields are active for use on Timesheets via the Timesheet Manager, Employee Portal and Approver Pages. When FALSE, there will only be one set of Break fields available on Timesheets.
CustomField.label: Display Break 2
